 9 Juli , 1916 Sunday We arriv at Oghratina OK about 6 last night took up our posit in the same old place at dawn the differ Regt move out , one to Saqia the other to Debabi then commenc there advanc on Oghratina burn clear all the Hod on the way in veri soon a huge ring of fire were to be seen the 2nd Regt got 5 prison at Saqia anoth five got away , they be too fast for our hors , they run up the bank slide down the other side while the hors have to go round , we finish up at 2 pm we had a great signal station on the old battlefield were in touch in all direct . Move back to Romani at dusk got in amongst our tea at 11.30 . Tire out 10 Juli , 1916 Monday 91 wks from home Reveill at 5 Had a quiet day today , noth do , the men went down for a swim after dinner it went great , plenti of surf etc , the hors enjoy it even more than we sever of them you could not get out of the water . Got home in time for tea then wrote letter to home . Nelson communic were up to putti again yesterday an inquiri is to be made into it today as to how he employ his signal what he did with them . All other unit OK especi the third .
